    <string name="tv_text_1">Welcome to the Pandout. This app is intended for record training.  Here you can see a brief instruction how to use it.</string>
    <string name="tv_text_2">This is your start page. In order to add a new exercise press the 'plus' button. You will see dialog box which is shown below.</string>
    <string name="tv_text_3">Red circle shows the optimal number of words in the title, but it is not required.</string>
    <string name="tv_text_4">For example: enter workout name - 'pullups', weight (kilograms) - '10', Approaches (amount) - '15', Repetition (repeat) - '3'.</string>
    <string name="tv_text_5">Make a long click on the item.</string>
    <string name="tv_text_6">In order to cancel an action click on any part of the screen or make a long click on another exercise</string>
    <string name="tv_text_7">If you want to change weight, name or another part of an exercise, make the same click</string>
    <string name="tv_text_8">Pay attention that weight, repetition, approaches must contain only numbers!</string>
